{"tid":1533433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個9月我要同奶共商場黨鐵攬炒！！","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:01:42.000Z","uid":38991,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"052e23998ee41fb80a34bff0c6a0cc298f9398cf","tid":1533433,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"成個連登一個行動post都無 on99<br />\n我唯有拋舊磚出黎比大家討論下<br />\n<br />\n既然黑警唔比人遊行，我地不如<span style=\"color: red;\">9月7號</span>去奶共商場涼下冷氣，做返良好市民，迫爆商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地咁多人 要行街梗係揀大商場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />\t自己行返自己個區啦<br />\n<br />\n九東: 德福 黨鐵總部<br />\n九西: 海港城 做開遊客生意老闆又大大聲撐警<br />\n<br />\n香港: 時代，同上<br />\n<br />\n1. 自備食水，唔可以係商場消費<br />\n2. 人多行唔到坐係地下我都無計<br />\n3. 來回交通跳閘爆黨鐵站呢d犯法野我唔會叫人做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重點: 討論行動咪撚再討論流言呀屌你老母！！！！成個9月無行動呀！！！</span>"},{"pid":"ce09b7d194ee6f110a3b7cdd849e563b4b900eb8","tid":1533433,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:17:31.000Z","msg":"9月8日都有行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tB7eQky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtB7eQky.jpg&h=01613123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dt4dkj5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDt4dkj5.png&h=d03e935b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9月8日(星期日)<br />\n美國領事館(遊行路線待定) <br />\n<br />\n唱住美國國歌 (最好揮埋國旗) <br />\n全力支持通過<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n[全登集氣]推到民陣搞，9月8號星期日大遊行，援請通過香港人權法！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531140</a><br />\n<br />\n美國人權及民主法案大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARgCLoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARgCLoO.jpg&h=045fa316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住練定美國國歌到時唱！！！！<br />\n </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Click個play制聽下先啦！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundcloud.com/iahc/usa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundcloud.com%2Fiahc%2Fusa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=d268abf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundcloud.com/iahc/usa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Donald Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNfTjAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNfTjAM.gif&h=db1663f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">聽手足唱既版本真係會聽到流馬尿</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F